Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.76,0:02:31.73,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.73,0:02:34.31,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I do it well?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.31,0:02:35.82,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Same here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.65,0:02:39.01,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noeru-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.88,0:02:46.84,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs65\pos(640,102.5)}Rainy Season Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.88,0:02:46.84,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs65\pos(640,681.25)}Quartz Rainbow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.53,0:02:48.73,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have your wallet with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:49.51,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.51,0:02:50.42,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your ID?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.42,0:02:51.05,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.05,0:02:51.76,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Handkerchief?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.76,0:02:52.39,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.39,0:02:53.05,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tissue?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.05,0:02:53.45,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.45,0:02:54.30,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Map?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.30,0:02:54.97,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.97,0:02:55.57,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Compass?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.57,0:02:56.30,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.30,0:02:57.37,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Carry-on food?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:02:57.79,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.79,0:02:58.79,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Helmet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.79,0:02:59.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.54,0:03:00.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pistol?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.33,0:03:02.13,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hand grenade?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:07.30,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a joke, Kana-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.14,0:03:10.59,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I was so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.59,0:03:13.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were relaxed enough to think about it, you would have understood it immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.26,0:03:16.14,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just mean, Rio-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.24,0:03:21.65,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Recently, you two have been so friendly to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.10,0:03:26.06,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio, you really look like a worried mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.93,0:03:29.95,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. This is your list for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.62,0:03:37.58,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. Today's mission is to go to town and purchase the things on the list. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.58,0:03:38.16,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:41.62,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, please drive safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.51,0:03:46.96,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Departure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.67,0:03:55.10,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(645,80)\c&H7EE6E8&\fs40}Pot Au Feu is French beef stew, a type of European hotpot.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.67,0:03:55.10,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come back early! We have "Pot Au Feu" for dinner!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:57.26,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come straight home!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.73,0:03:58.08,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She really is a mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.67,0:04:06.96,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This will be our first visit to the town, right, Noeru-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.96,0:04:07.81,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mmhmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:13.07,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But actually, this is like my first visit to the town...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.78,0:04:17.36,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.96,0:04:20.30,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.01,0:04:26.71,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's totally different from the time at the water festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.07,0:04:30.36,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The town has calmed down a lot. It's quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.06,0:04:41.16,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow ow ow ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.16,0:04:44.86,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The first one is Nue, the proud roof decorator of Torowa.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.86,0:04:47.42,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It serves to ward off evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.77,0:04:55.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The drinking fountain is next to it. That is the model of the 12th king of the Republic of Helvetia, King Akira Arukaria II.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:00.95,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Arrival.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.46,0:05:04.26,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, the one just now was...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.26,0:05:06.81,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm. I was told that, so we could drive safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.66,0:05:09.82,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah-huh, thank you, I got it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.82,0:05:12.46,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noeru-chan, you really know a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:17.93,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.51,0:05:23.02,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you decide whether you're coming in or not? You are disturbing my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.92,0:05:29.08,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! You're the lady from the water festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.08,0:05:30.90,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Big sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.40,0:05:33.86,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be ill-tempered.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.22,0:05:37.66,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really stubborn, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.66,0:05:39.99,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then at least call me Naomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.58,0:05:42.41,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Naomi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:56.46,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So you mean, the next shipment will be next month?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:57.31,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:06:00.91,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, does that girl know about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.31,0:06:03.41,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.91,0:06:11.12,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You girls are still weird, despite being soldiers...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:11.73,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.73,0:06:13.10,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:14.65,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.90,0:06:21.33,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were also interested in it the first time you came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.27,0:06:30.16,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me, can I touch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:42.52,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A-flat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:51.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a fish, right? What is its name?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.54,0:06:53.39,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...That is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.39,0:06:54.32,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.59,0:06:56.16,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.16,0:07:00.67,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a dolphin, a type of living creature, which was closer to us humans than fishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.67,0:07:04.10,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a sea-dwelling mammal from back when there were still living things in the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.10,0:07:06.21,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It...it was in the ocean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.17,0:07:08.42,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.42,0:07:10.04,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:17.76,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That guy is so skilled at making these.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:21.47,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the kind of person who doesn't look like an absolute romantic, but actually is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.47,0:07:23.99,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know him? The one who made these?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.99,0:07:26.76,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He has a large studio just outside of town.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:29.62,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All the glass items that we have are his products.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.32,0:07:34.06,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I really want to see where he makes all of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.06,0:07:35.02,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.02,0:07:35.77,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.30,0:07:38.26,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We are going there anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.32,0:07:47.77,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? The glass factory produces parts for the Takemicaduchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.77,0:07:52.25,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Naomi is also collecting parts from the old time for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.75,0:07:56.93,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Noeru-chan, you are really great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.93,0:07:59.93,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can fix such a complex machine in that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.93,0:08:01.08,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.76,0:08:07.87,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I can remember the secret chord of the signal horn, my head feels as if it's about to split.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.64,0:08:11.77,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not...that...difficult
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.12,0:08:16.77,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,because...a machine won't betray you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.70,0:08:20.21,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noeru-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:22.95,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are. Your change is 2,750,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.95,0:08:25.77,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh!? We get that much back?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.40,0:08:29.57,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it wrong. The change should be 2.75 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:33.02,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still like that, Noeru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.87,0:08:34.96,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your change.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.85,0:08:36.96,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.25,0:08:39.91,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The recent sound of the horn in the morning, was it by you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.91,0:08:41.61,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.61,0:08:44.07,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still very unskilled... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.07,0:08:47.16,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's good! I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.16,0:08:50.22,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I say it... It completely wakes me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.15,0:09:03.25,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I must improve at it as soon as possible so that I don't cause trouble for the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.19,0:09:13.75,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya, you're so cunning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.25,0:09:16.08,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't feel good, then come after me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:16.87,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.74,0:09:20.22,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ou-ou-ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:21.30,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm sorr...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.80,0:09:25.33,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! You got hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:27.08,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.72,0:09:29.97,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh!? You are...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.08,0:09:32.86,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl from the festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.08,0:09:32.86,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The clumsy girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.75,0:09:36.13,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel safe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:38.86,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like you've recovered from your illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.68,0:09:52.87,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You murderer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.63,0:09:58.38,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seiya-san! These people have no relation to your parents, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.38,0:10:01.46,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You people are all the same! I hate the military the most!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.74,0:10:03.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave town as soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.35,0:10:06.52,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You blow your horn poorly every morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:07.78,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You are so annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.32,0:10:11.01,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Seiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.57,0:10:14.95,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am really very sorry. That was so rude...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.95,0:10:16.16,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.16,0:10:19.04,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That boy is an orphan of the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.04,0:10:22.06,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that, whenever he sees soldiers...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.84,0:10:25.09,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noeru-chan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.49,0:10:30.21,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. It's true; we are soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.29,0:10:32.49,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.30,0:10:34.61,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noeru-chan.
