Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:12.82,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. We are soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.46,0:11:19.55,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was commissioned, I repeated the Oath of Paradores, and I thought I understood it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.23,0:11:23.34,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.34,0:11:25.65,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I understood it from the beginning, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.65,0:11:27.96,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't hesitate at this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.34,0:11:35.60,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. I must be prepared by getting better.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.60,0:11:39.01,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If there is no signal horn, it will bother the people.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:39.95,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We can see it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.85,0:11:45.74,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the glass factory?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.67,0:11:48.39,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's so great, Noeru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:51.57,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen a building that big until now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.67,0:12:15.26,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This one isn't good either? So the problem is the aberration?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.26,0:12:18.17,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure the refractive index is correct...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.41,0:12:30.45,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I am Sorami Kanata, a recruit. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.42,0:12:34.55,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.55,0:12:38.20,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, how was the timing before the error occured?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.20,0:12:40.39,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There is almost no change in seek time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.39,0:12:44.94,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The distortion at the edge of the image sensor is a little smaller than the last time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.69,0:12:44.71,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.11,0:12:50.50,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When the boss is working, he won't notice anything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.50,0:12:53.72,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Karl-oyajisan is a great guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.60,0:13:00.23,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He is one of only five people in the nation with the Meister title. He is a great craftsman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.23,0:13:05.23,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He won an important competition, and even presented his work to the Grand Duke.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.15,0:13:10.23,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maria, if you have time to chat, then go ahead and work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.23,0:13:13.20,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! I'm sorry, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.70,0:13:17.44,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't deserve to be called "Meister" at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:20.20,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any idea of how to fix this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.55,0:13:22.82,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:25.50,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The lens for Takemicaduchi's optical sensor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.34,0:13:27.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the original copy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.14,0:13:33.43,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to repair Takemicaduchi, two identical lens are needed, so I asked him to make copies of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.75,0:13:35.74,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, it hasn't been going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.74,0:13:37.55,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, they're so beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.81,0:13:45.51,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides silicon dioxide, which is the lens' main component, we still need to mix it with thorium oxide and magnesium oxide.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.51,0:13:51.66,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With those, we can do chromatic aberration and surrounding aberration. In other words, correct the distorted image.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.12,0:13:54.90,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, we don't know the ratio.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.44,0:14:00.66,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because this is a magic product from the old time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.87,0:14:10.17,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought glass was just beautiful, but it's complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:21.02,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because high-quality silicates can be collected in Seize, there are a lot of small studios focusing on handicrafts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.60,0:14:24.82,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This factory used to be one of those studios too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.17,0:14:31.10,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, as the war became tougher, glass products for the military became more important
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.59,0:14:35.44,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and this factory expanded during the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.85,0:14:52.39,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata, I love machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:57.61,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, machines can also hurt people.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.63,0:15:02.89,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemicaduchi must have killed a lot of people in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.75,0:15:11.20,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that a machine that killed people in the past must be scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.54,0:15:23.41,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But the scary ones are not the machines. It's the people that used them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.35,0:15:29.64,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because, because, like this horn. When I am blowing it, it's that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.64,0:15:32.81,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But when Rio-senpai blows the horn, it sings really beautifully.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.81,0:15:34.84,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tanks must be the same, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:44.27,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And a few days ago, Rio-senpai let me listen to Takemicaduchi's song.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.27,0:15:46.67,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It can sing so beautifully.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:03.37,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Takemicaduchi must have been a good tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.54,0:16:13.62,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. This time, let's...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.46,0:16:21.82,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noeru-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:24.55,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let her sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:30.39,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She must have stayed up all night again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.86,0:16:35.46,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noeru-chan is working really hard to repair Takemicaduchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.46,0:16:36.57,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.09,0:16:40.27,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl is a hardcore artisan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.27,0:16:45.12,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, I wouldn't even accept such a job of making something so troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:49.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are. Put this on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:51.15,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:55.61,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, you went to the Windmill, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:16:57.53,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Naomi-san alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.55,0:17:03.59,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. She said your boss is absolutely romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.59,0:17:07.18,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems so. That's good right, boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.46,0:17:11.27,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Go do your work immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.65,0:17:13.87,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! You are angry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.87,0:17:15.27,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Work, work...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.91,0:17:27.01,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, was the technology of the past that great?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.01,0:17:28.35,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.68,0:17:32.22,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, the boss has always said...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:36.95,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"No matter how great it was, it was still made by human beings!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.95,0:17:40.05,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"We must be able to make it!"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.59,0:17:42.22,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You believe the same thing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.22,0:17:45.30,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...Even though I want to say that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.60,0:17:52.27,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.64,0:17:57.44,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Rio-san's horn is a lot different than yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.44,0:18:02.13,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been worrying all the time. How can I become like senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.66,0:18:05.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I decided to practice hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.54,0:18:09.36,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See. My lips are so swollen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.14,0:18:11.49,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.04,0:18:16.90,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how I blow, I can never blow out something that sounds like senpai's music.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.44,0:18:20.58,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, I don't have talent...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.58,0:18:21.45,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.45,0:18:22.05,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.28,0:18:26.41,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Talent is the worst excuse someone's ever come up with for quitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.84,0:18:27.96,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Give that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.61,0:18:31.01,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Though I don't understand horns very well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.20,0:18:37.19,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know young people often fail here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:41.02,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Girl, are you trying to force the sound to come out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:14.79,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't intend to make it into this kind of shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.79,0:19:18.85,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Glass tends to form into this shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.09,0:19:29.66,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much, Karl!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.16,0:20:02.65,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let it sound like what it wants to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.21,0:20:51.53,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.02,0:20:53.24,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.24,0:20:57.53,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like the sun is rising a little earlier just for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.82,0:21:01.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That girl is also hardcore. The sound is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.18,0:21:04.54,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.35,0:21:15.76,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Glass is composed of different elements at different ratios. The slightest difference can change its sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.76,0:21:22.78,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we can't hear the difference, someone with a strong auditory sense should be able to perceive it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.97,0:21:28.85,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let Kanata help me find the sample with the closest sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.85,0:21:30.83,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In this way, probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.83,0:21:35.28,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, listen to its sound for us, girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.28,0:21:36.57,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.22,0:22:00.04,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Noeru-chan, it's changed a lot since you started here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.04,0:22:01.17,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.17,0:22:02.22,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.88,0:22:26.71,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it! You did it, Noeru-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.64,0:22:33.21,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.65,0:22:42.22,Sora Eng dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've seen Noeru smile.
